{"tid":449609,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果中國幫Apps改名：Finder變訪達、Clips變可立拍","createTime":"2017-10-27T10:33:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T11:32:35.000Z","uid":14953,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7835d984ce1ec124f00db05a3556dfd16129e015","tid":449609,"uid":14953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:33:52.000Z","msg":"為解決 iPhone 在大中華地區銷量下跌情況，蘋果在 7 月任命新總經理。有消息指蘋果想出令 iPhone、Macbook 更「親民」的方法，就是為蘋果生態系統裡面各種 Apps 改中文名！例如 Clips 將會改名為「可立拍」、Finder 會改名為「訪達」、Live Photo會變成「實況照片」、AirDrop會被改成「隔空投送」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/IMG_0980.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2FIMG_0980.png&h=57b455a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算在日本，所有蘋果 Apps 的名字都要清一色用英文，不過蘋果中國似乎有「特權」改變現狀。根據大陸傳媒消息指，蘋果將在未來推出的 iOS、watchOS 以及 macOS 三大系統的 Apps 當中，配上相應的中文名稱。這一堆中文名稱是來自蘋果中國的創意團隊，「是一項醞釀已久的操作」。目的主要是令中國一般消費者在購買蘋果產品時，毋須費力於識別英文名稱。消息指改名涉及數百處系統介面以及內置 Apps，目前只限於簡體中文語言介面，「是中國內地用戶獨享的待遇」，其他國家地區暫時沒有類似行動。<br />\n<br />\n根據消息引述蘋果的說法，改名主要分三種類型，包括直譯型、中英混合型，以及創意翻譯型，另外一些介面、App名字將保留英文。<br />\n<br />\niOS/watchOS：<br />\nSafari &rarr; Safari 瀏覽器<br />\nWallet &rarr; 錢包<br />\nFacetime &rarr; Facetime 通話<br />\nClips &rarr; 可立拍<br />\nGargeBand &rarr; 庫樂隊<br />\niMovie &rarr; iMovie 剪輯<br />\nTouch ID &rarr; 觸控 ID<br />\nFace ID &rarr; 面容 ID<br />\nAnimoji &rarr; 動活表情<br />\n<br />\nmacOS： Mission Control &rarr; 調度中心<br />\nDock &rarr; 程序塢<br />\nLaunchpad &rarr; 啟動台<br />\nFinder &rarr; 訪達<br />\nSpotlight &rarr; 聚焦<br />\nAirDrop &rarr; 隔空投送<br />\nAirPlay &rarr; 隔空播放<br />\nDock &rarr; 程序塢<br />\nTime Machine &rarr; 時間機器<br />\niCloud Drive &rarr; iCloud 雲盤<br />\niMessage &rarr; iMessage 信息<br />\n<br />\n保持不變的有Siri 以及 Appstore。前者因為已經全球通用，而且中國用戶亦習慣了使用「hi Siri」來呼叫語音控制，所以不作改變。而 App Store 亦因為已廣為人知的原因，所以不作更名。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/09-1024x560.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2F09-1024x560.jpg&h=8b95f082&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n資料來源：鳳凰科技<br />\nLink:<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/10/27/appleapps-2/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F10%2F27%2Fappleapps-2%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=ueduJ9UI%2FfU5gbN3igvYfqS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=c4db6fa6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/10/27/appleapps-2/mobile-phone/</a>"},{"pid":"d698bf64515fc144f9ec34bcefcfb42e5fb71dc0","tid":449609,"uid":14953,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:34:49.000Z","msg":"英文都唔識就唔好學人用Apple 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c8adc941f9a2cda29cf498410d4d956ffae99b4","tid":449609,"uid":44454,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:36:29.000Z","msg":"Siri呢"},{"pid":"6784c20d41897141ddf4374bdccf59af2f83f38d","tid":449609,"uid":19275,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:39:39.000Z","msg":"中國真係人蠢不突止重要全世界就翻佢地智商<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解咁撚蠢又可以咁撚有錢"},{"pid":"ffda7ae77b20172eba902d366328b391cd9a08f1","tid":449609,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:44:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Siri呢</blockquote><br />\n舌脷"},{"pid":"47e4d957cff2f9a2bf4f0913c721362a48408b17","tid":449609,"uid":37735,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:49:07.000Z","msg":"apple 奶共力真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又係中國設雲端中心<br />\n又更貼心服務"},{"pid":"a3553424c1547e9293669c59de7e9ae5296145d4","tid":449609,"uid":14953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T11:10:15.000Z","msg":"講真，唔識英文都識認個icon logo 啦，有幾難明啊?"},{"pid":"a5943547cace60a25b41b9c8d48a886e9752703b","tid":449609,"u